ğŸ”¹ Part 4: Architecture Overview
âœ… Angular (Frontend SPA Framework)
ğŸ“˜ Core Concepts:

Components = UI blocks

Modules = Group of components

Services = Shared logic (API calls)

Routing = Navigation between views

ğŸ¨ Angular is a Single Page Application framework. It renders dynamic content without reloading the whole page.


ğŸ”— Angular Architecture Explained

âœ… ASP.NET Core MVC (Backend Web Framework)
ğŸ“˜ Core Concepts:

Model = Represents your data

View = HTML with Razor syntax

Controller = Handles user request

ğŸ“˜ It's a server-side framework that generates HTML dynamically and returns it to browser.

